name: SpritzMoon
description:
SpritzMoon Crypto Token (SpritzMoon), totally made in Italy, is a Crypto DeFi developed on Binance BlockChain  (BSC).SpritzMoon has 3 objectives to develop:
1. Create a Community within which to develop creating economic value
2. Sociality is one of the strengths of this Crypto with concrete aid to the various associations related to the Spritz theme with a view to prevention
3. Allow all members of the community to use the token for Weekend Spritz with Friends in Community SpritzMoon Bar
